title: NARS Blush, Taj Mahal
description: Made with transparent pigments for a soft and sheer look. Imparts a natural, healthy glow for any skin tone and may be worn alone or layered together for more depth and intensity.

title: Tarte Amazonian Clay Finishing Powder
description: Product Performance: This translucent, silky finishing powder keeps makeup in place without ever appearing chalky. It mattifies skin by removing excess surface oil. This powder can even be used alone as a treatment to reap all the benefits of Amazonian clay.  Powered By: Amazonian clay: Amazonian clay acts as a total skin balancer, by hydrating all skin types, reducing the appearance of dry, flaky skin, improving clarity and texture, and removing surface oil to mattify skin for a soft focus and flawless finish.

description: Revlon Just bitten kissing balm stain provides a gorgeous flush of color and the moisturizing comfort of a balm in a portable, self sharpening chubby crayon.

title: ecoTOOLS Make-Up Kabuki Brush Set

title: The Balm In Stain Blush, Houndstooth Mauve, .3 Ounce
description: Shadow and blush 0.3 ounce the subtle shimmer catches the eye while the warm undertones provide a glow that is oh-so natural. A powder that works as both eye shadow and blush.

title: Too Faced Cosmetics Absolutely Invisible Candlelight Powder, 0.32-Ounce
description: Capture the ethereal glow and ultra flattering light of a romantic candlelit dinner, anytime.
